{"tid":2203214,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"副董事長林斌狂沽3.5億股小米套現78億港元","createTime":"2020-09-15T07:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T12:32:29.000Z","uid":225931,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"03962654289d07792b230e821aebc6b26f252b8c","tid":2203214,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T07:43:34.000Z","msg":"小米 （01810） 聯合創始人、副董事長林斌再減持集團股份套現近80億元。林斌在上次不減持承諾期完結後僅一個月即再減持，加上選擇在小米剛染藍的時候沽貨，消息利淡短期股價。不過今次套現後，林斌承諾5年內不再減持手上股份，消除了市場對短期再減持的憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n林斌以每股22.55元作價減持3.5億股小米股份。受聯合創始人減持的消息影響，小米股價今早曾低見22.35元，一度失守配股價，其後重上配股價。小米半日報22.65元，跌約4%，並拖低恒指跌逾30點，是拖累恒指最勁的股藍籌"},{"pid":"6c1341c1715d9ee1bba4be42b2d795d545ed6155","tid":2203214,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T07:45:18.000Z","msg":"財經台"},{"pid":"a76fb230ce3482bbed8301df537220baef17e8a7","tid":2203214,"uid":15605,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T07:48:24.000Z","msg":"黑警仲唔去拉人"},{"pid":"7974ede75316199febbd58b32f74b7cb30d64959","tid":2203214,"uid":293494,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T07:59:09.000Z","msg":"副董事長都沽。。。"},{"pid":"1b21d60cfbe8b980448c82204eab252ff8a0d86f","tid":2203214,"uid":32403,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:01:13.000Z","msg":"佢減持完手上仲揸住10%股份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b983da39ffa3ed10d6354bafdeeb8b6a13678333","tid":2203214,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b21d60cfbe8b980448c82204eab252ff8a0d86f","tid":2203214,"uid":32403,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:01:13.000Z","msg":"佢減持完手上仲揸住10%股份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:06:34.000Z","msg":"2.2%既10%即係around 0.2%<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6bb0a54fc79022611e4041bbc05b591e31031d","tid":2203214,"uid":131323,"like":3,"dis